replies.body:
Just replace it with a flat heal that scales with low HP;

> Karma heals for **40/80/120/160HP** (+1 per 50AP), increased by **3%** for every 1% of her missing HP. 

There. Satisfying to level, more balanced for Tank Karma and actually useful for Mage Karma. We could also get rid of that confused bonus root, while we are at it...
